title: Brisbane Club
body:
Hi guys,

Just seeing if there would be any interest in a club for Brisbane residents? Would be nice to play games, with the potential to go out socially (hah) on occasion.

Hit me up if keen - IGN 'Project Icarus'

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

replies.body: Threw you an in game add I'm keen for some more Brisbane peeps to play with
Up for at least local players with a possibility of social gatherings.
